Creating New Folder on VSCODE local
Go to root folder jsmmc
create bicte3 folder using mkdir bicte3

Init Command
  Init - used to create a new git repo
   git init  (after create folder on remote)
   git remote add origin <-link>
   git remote -v (to verify remote)
   git branch (to check branch)
   git branch -M main (to rename branch)
   git push -u origin main (to setup upstream)

   -------------------------------------
   Branch Commands
   git branch ( to check branch)
   git branch -M main ( to rename branch)
   git checkout <-branch name-> (to navigate)
   git checkout -b <-new branch name-> (to create the new branch)
   git branch -d <-branch name-> (to delete the branch)